## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **sulbactam-durlobactam Xacduro 2023** = first FDA-approved CRAB-targeted therapy (HABP/VABP). carbapenem-resistant Acinetobacter baumannii 가 IDSA Tier-1 critical-priority pathogen. quantum-VQE 의 PBP3 + class A/C/D β-lactamase dual-binding scaffold 가 직접 fit.
2. **cefiderocol Fetroja 2019** = siderophore Trojan-horse Fe-uptake mechanism — multidrug-resistant Gram-neg (CRE + CRAB + CR-Pseudomonas) 가 outer-membrane porin-loss escape 못 함. quantum-VQE 의 Fe-chelator + cephalosporin-warhead 결합 modeling.
3. **ceftazidime-avibactam + meropenem-vaborbactam + imipenem-relebactam 2015-2019** = β-lactamase inhibitor 3종 paradigm — diazabicyclooctane (avibactam) + cyclic boronate (vaborbactam) + DBO (relebactam) — KPC carbapenemase 시대 대응. NDM/VIM/IMP metallo-β-lactamase 는 여전히 unmet.
4. **eravacycline + plazomicin + omadacycline 2018** = tetracycline + aminoglycoside modernization — efflux + ribosome protection 우회.
5. **lefamulin Xenleta 2019** = first systemic pleuromutilin — 50S P-site novel mechanism. CABP 적응증 (HAI 직접 X). 향후 nosocomial 적응증 expansion 가능성.
6. **zoliflodacin Phase 3 2024** = first novel oral DNA gyrase B (spiropyrimidinetrione) — single-dose gonorrhea — fluoroquinolone-resistance escape. nosocomial gonococcal infection adjunct.
7. **bezlotoxumab + Vowst + Rebyota + bacteriophage** = "non-antibiotic" HAI tool 4종 — TcdB mAb + FMT capsule + FMT enema + 개인화 phage. C. difficile + CRE/CRAB compassionate-use cross-microbiome.
8. **ibrexafungerp + rezafungin 2021-2023** = first oral triterpenoid + once-weekly echinocandin — Candida auris + invasive candidemia. 진균 nosocomial 의 첫 oral + first long-acting echinocandin.
9. **WHO AWaRe + ASP** = framework-level — Access (1L) / Watch (escalation) / Reserve (last-line) 분류 + antibiotic stewardship. clinical-epidemiology layer (drug-target-axis 외).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, HAI + MDRO 임상 의미 한정. 신규 carbapenem-class + dual β-lactamase inhibitor 가 in-vivo PK/PD + nephrotoxicity 우회 검증 필수.

